<UserControl
    x:Class="GTA5OnlineTools.Views.ReadMe.GTAHax"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    d:DesignHeight="600"
    d:DesignWidth="1100"
    Style="{StaticResource UserControlStyle_Loaded}"
    mc:Ignorable="d">

    <UniformGrid Columns="2">
        <RichTextBox Margin="5,5,2.5,5" Style="{StaticResource RichTextBoxStyle_ReadMe}">
            <FlowDocument>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Title}">
                    简介
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● 一个GTA5全局变量编辑器
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● 修改数据分为int类型和bool类型。字符串格式一般为$+MP0/MP1+_对应变量名
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● int类型可以直接修改，赋值为整数型，如果标明范围则不要超过，否则可能会有风险
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● bool类型需要人物佩戴一个可下拉式头盔来表示修改状态，头盔上拉表示true，头盔下拉表示false
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    项目地址：<Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.unknowncheats.me/forum/grand-theft-auto-v/461672-gtahax-1-67-external-thread-3-a.html" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://www.unknowncheats.me/forum/grand-theft-auto-v/461672-gtahax-1-67-external-thread-3-a.html</Hyperlink>
                </Paragraph>

                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Title}">
                    更多
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● 详细使用教程，请前往小助手官方网站查看&#160;<Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://crazyzhang.cn" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">https://crazyzhang.cn</Hyperlink>
                </Paragraph>

            </FlowDocument>
        </RichTextBox>
        <!--  ////////////////////  -->
        <RichTextBox Margin="2.5,5,5,5" Style="{StaticResource RichTextBoxStyle_ReadMe}">
            <FlowDocument>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Title}">
                    说明
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● 比如我们要修改角色的属性值-体力，如果角色是角色1为MP0，角色2为MP1，对应的函数为SCRIPT_INCREASE_STAM，赋值范围为0~100，则最终组合字符串为
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    $MP0_SCRIPT_INCREASE_STAM<LineBreak />
                    100</Paragraph>
                <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource ParagraphStyle_Content}">
                    ● 这样就代表我们修改了角色1的属性值体力为100，也就是加满了体力
                </Paragraph>
            </FlowDocument>
        </RichTextBox>
    </UniformGrid>

</UserControl>
